  "instructions": [
    "In a large pot heat 2 tablespoons of sesame oil over medium heat.",
    "Brown the pork belly in batches until crispy on all sides, then set aside.",
    "Add 2 cloves of garlic and 1 inch of ginger to the pot and saut\u000639 until fragrant.",
    "Add the soy sauce, coconut sugar, and 200ml of water to the pot and bring to a boil.",
    "Return the pork belly to the pot and simmer for 2 hours, or until tender.",
    "Meanwhile, combine the grated ginger, minced garlic, chopped scallions, and citrus zest in a bowl.",
    "Mix in the truffle oil, soy sauce, and sesame oil.",
    "To assemble the dish, place a portion of the braised pork in a scallop shell, then top with a spoonful of the citrus sauce.",
    "Garnish with chopped green onions and serve immediately."
  ],
